{"tid":2185507,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仇栩欣【眾籌私人檢控濫暴警】","createTime":"2020-09-02T10:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:38:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"34fb45354b002cd1c7d99b748ec5c2dac37d9fa6","tid":2185507,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"仇栩欣【眾籌私人檢控濫暴警】<br />\n<br />\n我的襲警案於8月11日判決，法庭明確指出該警察使用施以不恰當武力，要求將事件紀錄在案。縱雖如此，律政司並未有採取任何行動，彰顯公義。判決之後，有不少市民希望我能夠就事件作出追究，讓濫暴的人能夠正確及公平地被檢控。在尋求法律意見後，我決定向該名警員提出私人檢控，並就相關法律開支進行眾籌。懇請各位香港人仗義相助！<br />\n<br />\n我的眾籌目標為110萬港元（包括眾籌和付款平台收取約10%即約10萬元費用）。在完全支付訴訟和審計有關費用後，餘款將全數捐予612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%bf%ab%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e7%259c%25be%25e7%25b1%258c%25e7%25a7%2581%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%25bf%25ab%25e6%259a%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2593%25a1%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXEXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=454821aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%bf%ab%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKmGz2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKmGz2L.jpg&h=9dd39df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n捐咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfSKxV7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfSKxV7.png&h=771355d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n仇栩欣及助理襲警罪脫 官斥警「大話冚大話」 關注警方使用不當武力<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2152874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2152874</a><br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RwP2rWN8HGG7qqUZldzE9B3BNTo=/1183x839/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJRNYVVP2FEPXBDXU2PWLBAYDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRwP2rWN8HGG7qqUZldzE9B3BNTo%3D%2F1183x839%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJRNYVVP2FEPXBDXU2PWLBAYDQ.png&h=c33951bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月中旬，去年民變期間兩宗案件定讞，頗足顯示香港公安的質素。第一宗是北角區議員仇栩欣案。根據現場錄影，兩名公安見仇栩欣在拍攝他們「維持治安」的手段，上前冷冷問道：「拍完了沒有？」他們隨即出手，襲擊仇栩欣，把她推倒地上，膝壓其身，手扼其頸，最後還控告她「襲警」。怪不得裁判官何俊堯判仇栩欣無罪，還指出：「警察與市民說話，態度怎麼這樣輕佻？兩名警察根本不是在正當執行職務，用武也不得其宜，還謊話連篇。當局應記錄在案。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200901/5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200901%2F5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXEXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=555160b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200901%2F5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI%2F&h=419d9a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200901/5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n==============="},{"pid":"0478e9fb2ba5526ac94c0f937180bec9b21e6535","tid":2185507,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%bf%ab%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e7%259c%25be%25e7%25b1%258c%25e7%25a7%2581%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%25bf%25ab%25e6%259a%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2593%25a1%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXEXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=454821aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%bf%ab%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1/</a><br />\n<br />\n56%Funded 20200902 18:05"},{"pid":"1d13ca6a585ac6727d6068a818c55a127c3a42a0","tid":2185507,"uid